<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> tiripuvaṉaccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrīrājarā<supplied reason="omitted">ja</supplied></hi> tevarkku yāṇṭu Irupatāvatu nāyaṉār tirukkā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḷattiuṭaiya ṉāyaṉārkku Īkkāṭṭukkoṭṭattuk kākkalūrnāṭṭup perumuḷaiyūruṭaiyār
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <note n="247-2">ā few letters are built in at the beginnings of lines 3 to 12.</note>ṭaiyāṉ makaṉ tevaṉāṉa ñāṉampeṟṟār Ivvāṇṭai taimmātattu tirumuṉpi
<lb n="4" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Eriyavaitta cantiviḷakku Oṉṟukku poliyūṭṭākac cantirātittavarai celva
<lb n="5" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kopālaṉmāṭai Iraṇṭu Immāṭai Iraṇṭum tiruviḷakkiṭaiyaril tirukkāḷattiu
<lb n="6" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ḻikkoṉum poṉṉaṉāṉa Irācanārāyaṇakkoṉum kālicāttaṉ tirumulakkoṉum kaik
<lb n="7" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vaṭukakkoṉ makaṉ vempakkoṉukku kuṭuttu Ivvempakkoṉeṉ Iccantiviḷakku O
<lb n="8" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Iraṇṭum poliyūṭṭāka nāṉ kaikkoṇṭu nāḷ Oṉṟukku tirukkāḷattiuṭaiyāṉā 
<lb n="9" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> nai cantirātittavarai Ikkoyiṟ civappirāmaṇarvacame nāṉum Eṉ vaṟkattuḷḷārum
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kkoṇṭeṉ vempakkoṉeṉ Ippaṭikku Ivai vempakkoṉ Eḻuttu Ivai cittira
<lb n="11" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Ivai Irācanārāyaṇakkoṉ Eḻuttu—ivai tirumulakkoṉ Eḻuttu Itu paṉmā<hi rend="grantha">heśva</hi> ra ra<hi rend="grantha">kṣai</hi>%
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> rumun Erikka ñāṉampeṟṟāṉ Iṭṭa tirukkuttuviḷakku Oṉṟināl Iruppu nārācam Uḻppaṭa pitta<note n="248-1">The continuation is built in.</note>
</p>

